          "taskStatus" : "SUCCESS",
          "status" : "SUCCESS",
          "results" : [
            {
              "message" : "<h1 id=\"marketing-campaign-data\">Marketing Campaign Data</h1>\n<p>This notebook creates the <code>CLIENTS</code>, <code>CONTACTS</code>, <code>PAST_CAMPAIGNS</code>, and <code>PROSPECTS</code>\ntables from CSV files in Object Storage, using <code>DBMS_CLOUD.COPY_DATA</code>.</p>\n<p>The data is derived from the UCI Bank Marketing dataset: 45,211 clients from a\nPortuguese bank's phone campaigns. Target: <code>subscribed</code> (term deposit, Y/N, ~11.7% Y).</p>\n<p><strong>Changes from the original data:</strong> split into separate tables keyed on a new\n<code>client_id</code>; columns renamed; <code>day</code> + <code>month</code> combined into <code>contact_date</code> with a\nsynthetic 2025 year; <code>unknown</code> values recoded as nulls; target recoded yes/no to Y/N.\n<code>prospects.csv</code> is our own addition, not part of the original data.</p>\n<h3 id=\"tables\">Tables</h3>\n<p><strong><code>CLIENTS</code></strong> (45,211 rows): client attributes. <code>age</code>, <code>job</code>, <code>marital</code>,\n<code>education</code>, <code>default_credit</code>, <code>balance</code> (avg yearly, EUR), <code>housing_loan</code>,\n<code>personal_loan</code>.</p>\n<p><strong><code>CONTACTS</code></strong> (45,211 rows): current campaign activity, from\n<code>current_campaign_contacts.csv</code>. <code>contact_type</code> (cellular/telephone),\n<code>contact_date</code>, <code>duration_seconds</code>, <code>contacts_during_campaign</code>, <code>subscribed</code>\n(target). Note: <code>duration_seconds</code> is only known after the call, so it leaks the\noutcome and should be excluded from predictive models.</p>\n<p><strong><code>PAST_CAMPAIGNS</code></strong> (45,211 rows): prior campaign history.\n<code>days_from_last_contact</code> (-1 = never contacted, ~37k rows), <code>previous_contacts</code>,\n<code>past_outcomes</code> (success/failure/other, null when no history).</p>\n<p><strong><code>PROSPECTS</code></strong> (100 rows): <code>client_id</code> list of 100 prospective customers to be\ntargeted in the next campaign.</p>\n<p>Copyright (c) 2026 Oracle Corporation</p>\n<h6 id=\"the-universal-permissive-license-upl-version-10\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://oss.oracle.com/licenses/upl/\">The Universal Permissive License (UPL), Version 1.0</a></h6>\n",
              "type" : "HTML"
            }
          ],
          "forms" : "[]"
        },
        "relations" : [ ],
        "dynamicFormParams" : "{}"
      },
      {
        "row" : 0,
        "col" : 0,
        "sizeX" : 0,
        "width" : 0,
        "title" : "Define Object Storage URI and drop tables if they exist",
        "hasTitle" : true,
        "message" : [
          "%script\r",
          "\r",
          "DECLARE\r",
          "   -- UPDATE THIS with your Object Storage path\r",
          "   base_uri VARCHAR2(500) := 'https://adwc4pm.objectstorage.us-ashburn-1.oci.customer-oci.com/p/Piij8udcadlzWjssUDJ4Y-_Bz8ZVYVQJ8W--T9YE0ULhT3kjeXhrHPNVj3wJjbkB/n/adwc4pm/b/OML-Resources/o/';\r",
          "   \r",
          "BEGIN\r",
          "   -- Drop existing tables if they exist\r",
          "   FOR t IN (SELECT table_name FROM user_tables \r",
          "             WHERE table_name IN ('CLIENTS','CONTACTS','PAST_CAMPAIGNS','PROSPECTS')) LOOP\r",
          "      EXECUTE IMMEDIATE 'DROP TABLE '||t.table_name||' CASCADE CONSTRAINTS';\r",
          "      DBMS_OUTPUT.PUT_LINE('Dropped table: ' || t.table_name);\r",
          "   END LOOP;\r",
          "END;"
        ],
        "selectedVisualization" : "raw",
        "visualizationConfig" : null,
        "hideCode" : false,
        "hideResult" : false,
        "hideGutter" : true,
        "hideVizConfig" : false,
        "hideInIFrame" : false,
